ComicInfo.Title: Return of the Jaguar Men Part One
ComicInfo.Summary:
Die Hard screenwriter Steven E. de Souza's critically acclaimed reboot of Will Eisner's Sheena, Queen of the Jungle comes to Moonstone in this action packed series! When archaeologists exploring ruins on Rachel Caldwell's remote jungle estate are found torn to bits, the authorities blame 'savage terrorist' Sheena. Rachel knows otherwise, since she is Sheena - but what she can't believe is the only remaining explanation, the curse of the Jaguar Men!
